          <p class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-xxs">02/04/2020</span>
            {% include '../svg/arrow-right-svg.twig' with {classes: 'text-white ease-in-out duration-300 transform group-hover:translate-x-3'} %}
          </p>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="h-40 xl:p-8 lg:p-6 md:p-4 p-3 flex flex-col justify-between group" style="background: #41b2ed;">
          <p class="text-md">Электронная рассылка журнала «Флебология»</p>
          <p class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-xxs">02/04/2020</span>
            {% include '../svg/arrow-right-svg.twig' with {classes: 'text-white ease-in-out duration-300 transform group-hover:translate-x-3'} %}
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-big bg-white shadow-my">
    <div class="container">

      <h3 class="append-line-to-right mb-6 mt-5 font-serif lg:text-4-25xl text-3-5xl text-purple-300">Новости</h3>

      <div class="md:mb-16 mb-10 grid md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-7 gap-8 text-blue-500">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-purple-300">
          <img data-src="./assets/images/index-news-img-1.png" alt="" class="md:h-56 h-64 w-full object-cover">

          <div class="inner-content md:mt-5 mt-3 pl-2">
            <span class="block mb-1 text-xxs">02/04/2020</span>

            <h6 class="text-md leading-tight">Перенос XIII Научно-практической конференции АФР в Ярославле </h6>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="#" class="hover:text-purple-300">
          <img data-src="./assets/images/index-news-img-2.png" alt="" class="md:h-56 h-64 w-full object-cover">

          <div class="inner-content md:mt-5 mt-3 pl-2">
            <span class="block mb-1 text-xxs">02/04/2020</span>

            <h6 class="text-md leading-tight">Гранты на конференцию АФР 2020 </h6>
          </div>
        </a>
         
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-purple-300">
          <img data-src="./assets/images/index-news-img-3.png" alt="" class="md:h-56 h-64 w-full object-cover">

